queries.sql: SELECT `s`.`img_url` as `gambar_service`, `pl`.`id_services` as `id`, `s`.`nama` as `nama_service`, (SUM(b.harga * pl.besar) + s.harga) as harga_total, `s`.`deskripsi` FROM `paket_layanan` `pl` JOIN `services` `s` ON `s`.`id` = `pl`.`id_services` JOIN `barang` `b` ON `b`.`id` = `pl`.`id_barang` GROUP BY `pl`.`id_services`

SELECT `s`.`img_url` as `gambar_service`, `pl`.`id_services` as `id`, `s`.`nama` as `nama_service`, (SUM(b.harga * pl.besar) + s.harga) as harga_total, `s`.`deskripsi` FROM `paket_layanan` `pl` JOIN `services` `s` ON `s`.`id` = `pl`.`id_services` JOIN `barang` `b` ON `b`.`id` = `pl`.`id_barang` JOIN `keranjang` `k` ON `k`.`id_paket_layanan` = `pl`.`id` JOIN `invoice` `i` ON `i`.`id` = `k`.`id_invoice` WHERE `i`.`user_username` = 'rizki' GROUP BY `pl`.`id_services`
